description: MYBSS054R6EBF is a boost-up isolated DC-DC converter for PSE of POE. The DC-DC converter is suitable for 12V input or 24V input such as an AD/DC adapter. It has got 54V/0.6A output, 10.8V to 27V input voltage range.
name: MYBSS054R6EBF
series_description: MYBSP series is boost-up isolated DC-DC converter for PoE especially PSE. It has got small, low profile and surface mount type.
series_headline: MYBSS series is boost-up isolated DC-DC converter for PoE especially PSE.
